1
00:00:49,184 --> 00:00:52,768
=In Love With Loving You=
(Based on Love by Erxi on Qimao)

2
00:00:52,768 --> 00:00:55,520
=Episode 14=

3
00:01:07,120 --> 00:01:09,359
I remember the Purple Glaze
was already shattered.

4
00:01:09,680 --> 00:01:12,760
But this one is completely intact.
How did you fix it?

5
00:01:13,200 --> 00:01:16,079
It was Mr. Song who found
two precious pieces

6
00:01:16,159 --> 00:01:19,159
of Purple Glaze in the sea
before the tsunami hit.

7
00:01:20,599 --> 00:01:22,959
It was Miss Ji who was deeply moved
by the sincere love

8
00:01:22,959 --> 00:01:24,519
between you and your wife.

9
00:01:24,920 --> 00:01:26,239
It gave me immense courage.

10
00:01:27,879 --> 00:01:30,840
The Purple Glaze
symbolizes eternal love.

11
00:01:31,280 --> 00:01:35,000
Thank you for restoring the shell lamp
my wife made with her own hands.

12
00:01:38,959 --> 00:01:39,879
Is three days enough?

13
00:01:42,040 --> 00:01:43,079
What do you mean?

14
00:01:44,040 --> 00:01:47,439
Don't you want to design a proposal?
How about three days?

15
00:01:47,680 --> 00:01:48,599
- Thank you, Mr. Yu.
- Thank you, Mr. Yu.

16
00:02:12,199 --> 00:02:12,704
(Song Group)

17
00:02:12,704 --> 00:02:15,159
All departments,
focus on your current tasks now.

18
00:02:18,120 --> 00:02:19,840
Sorry I'm late.

19
00:02:26,823 --> 00:02:28,680
(Song Zhaoli (Mr. Song))

20
00:02:28,680 --> 00:02:30,479
(You turned off my alarm?)

21
00:02:49,560 --> 00:02:51,159
(I figured you didn't sleep well,)

22
00:02:51,560 --> 00:02:52,680
(so I let you sleep longer.)

23
00:02:54,960 --> 00:02:56,199
By the way,

24
00:02:57,080 --> 00:02:59,960
our management rules
have been too lax lately.

25
00:03:00,120 --> 00:03:03,039
The project department
has its own clock-in time now?

26
00:03:05,000 --> 00:03:05,600
No.

27
00:03:07,800 --> 00:03:09,879
Then let's establish a penalty system.

28
00:03:10,800 --> 00:03:11,520
For example,

29
00:03:11,759 --> 00:03:13,759
200 yuan for each late arrival.

30
00:03:14,039 --> 00:03:16,360
Starting today, Miss Ji.

31
00:03:18,879 --> 00:03:19,552
Okay.

32
00:03:48,759 --> 00:03:52,199
(Turning off your alarm was my fault.
I'll pay the fine.)

33
00:04:08,840 --> 00:04:11,159
This artificial plant doesn't
look quite right, does it?

34
00:04:13,960 --> 00:04:16,199
He's not leaving until afternoon.
There's still time.

35
00:04:16,560 --> 00:04:18,680
How about we go outside
and pick some real ones?

36
00:04:22,208 --> 00:04:22,752
Let's go.

37
00:04:29,639 --> 00:04:31,120
I bet you don't have many whorls.

38
00:04:31,680 --> 00:04:32,279
Whorls?

39
00:04:33,240 --> 00:04:34,199
Haven't you heard?

40
00:04:34,680 --> 00:04:37,000
Fewer whorls you have,
you're more prone to lose them.

41
00:04:37,639 --> 00:04:38,879
The more whorls you have,

42
00:04:39,200 --> 00:04:41,480
the tighter you hold on
and never let go.

43
00:04:49,959 --> 00:04:51,839
See? Just like this.

44
00:05:04,040 --> 00:05:05,480
You've planted so many roses?

45
00:05:07,920 --> 00:05:08,639
Put it this way.

46
00:05:10,240 --> 00:05:12,720
What I like is exactly the same as you.

47
00:05:34,560 --> 00:05:35,959
- It should be fine.
- Right.

48
00:05:35,959 --> 00:05:37,040
We just need to glue it on.

49
00:05:51,566 --> 00:05:54,309
(Land Transfer Contract)

50
00:05:54,519 --> 00:05:56,839
Miss Ji, you failed your assessment.

51
00:05:57,680 --> 00:05:59,639
Your salary will be paid up to today.

52
00:06:00,519 --> 00:06:01,519
You may leave.

53
00:06:05,838 --> 00:06:08,959
(Song Group)

54
00:06:08,959 --> 00:06:10,319
It's the contract Mr. Yu sent us.

55
00:06:17,639 --> 00:06:18,304
Grandpa.

56
00:06:18,959 --> 00:06:22,519
Mr. Yu has agreed to sell us
the downtown land for 60 million yuan,

57
00:06:23,040 --> 00:06:25,560
allowing us to build
Qingcheng's largest art district.

58
00:06:42,279 --> 00:06:43,279
Miss Ji,

59
00:06:43,639 --> 00:06:47,720
your design is bold and innovative,
but it doesn't meet my expectations.

60
00:06:48,439 --> 00:06:51,839
My wife likes things
that are serene yet ever-changing.

61
00:06:52,439 --> 00:06:57,360
She often says a good artwork
is like the shimmering sea surface,

62
00:06:58,000 --> 00:07:00,879
containing all forms of beauty within.

63
00:07:01,959 --> 00:07:05,399
I've never found a designer
who truly understands her.

64
00:07:05,759 --> 00:07:07,759
Let's call off this collaboration.

65
00:07:12,319 --> 00:07:14,000
Like this, Mr. Yu?

66
00:07:39,120 --> 00:07:41,879
Grandpa, Ji Xuan
has passed the assessment.

67
00:07:42,240 --> 00:07:44,399
You should keep your word.

68
00:07:45,600 --> 00:07:48,240
Welcome to the Song Group, Miss Ji.

69
00:07:53,879 --> 00:07:54,800
Thank you, Chairman.

70
00:07:54,959 --> 00:07:56,120
I won't let you down.

71
00:08:00,319 --> 00:08:00,819
Qiu Lin.

72
00:08:01,120 --> 00:08:03,600
Have Finance
settle Miss Ji's commission.

73
00:08:03,920 --> 00:08:04,420
Yes.

74
00:08:08,319 --> 00:08:09,319
One more thing,

75
00:08:09,439 --> 00:08:11,579
during this collaboration with Mr. Yu,

76
00:08:11,579 --> 00:08:14,360
someone tried
to sabotage Miss Ji's work.

77
00:08:15,079 --> 00:08:16,240
Let me repeat it.

78
00:08:16,680 --> 00:08:18,519
If something like this happens again,

79
00:08:18,839 --> 00:08:22,439
no matter who you are,
get out of the Song Group.

80
00:08:24,920 --> 00:08:26,519
In fact, I should thank this person.

81
00:08:26,720 --> 00:08:30,160
If it weren't for her, I wouldn't have
such perfect backup plan.

82
00:08:36,679 --> 00:08:37,320
Dismissed.

83
00:08:44,840 --> 00:08:45,840
Any plans tonight?

84
00:08:46,000 --> 00:08:47,639
I've been bothering you all this time.

85
00:08:47,639 --> 00:08:48,679
I feel terribly sorry.

86
00:08:48,879 --> 00:08:50,000
Now the project is done,

87
00:08:50,000 --> 00:08:50,879
I'll move back.

88
00:08:51,480 --> 00:08:53,440
You can rest
in the master bedroom properly.

89
00:08:54,159 --> 00:08:54,879
Must you move?

90
00:08:57,000 --> 00:08:58,960
The locks were changed a while ago.

91
00:08:59,120 --> 00:08:59,759
I forgot it.

92
00:09:08,080 --> 00:09:12,159
By all rights, shouldn't you treat me
to dinner tomorrow night?

93
00:09:14,000 --> 00:09:16,559
I have plans with Wu Shu tomorrow night.
Maybe take a rain check.

94
00:09:23,559 --> 00:09:26,600
I'm celebrating with Ji Xuan.
Why are you here?

95
00:09:27,240 --> 00:09:28,080
Not your business.

96
00:09:29,559 --> 00:09:31,399
Look at Ji Xuan's cooking skills.

97
00:09:31,639 --> 00:09:33,600
And look at you, all you do is eat.

98
00:09:33,919 --> 00:09:35,799
Well, I'll take a picture and post it.

99
00:09:44,000 --> 00:09:46,879
Women can vary vastly.

100
00:09:47,041 --> 00:09:48,075
(Send)

101
00:09:55,480 --> 00:09:57,360
He is eating at Ji Xuan's place.

102
00:09:58,360 --> 00:09:59,720
What do you mean by that?

103
00:09:59,720 --> 00:10:00,600
Being sarcastic?

104
00:10:01,120 --> 00:10:02,799
I bet you know what it means.

105
00:10:05,147 --> 00:10:06,336
(Mr. Qiu likes)

106
00:10:06,639 --> 00:10:08,000
Mr. Qiu liked my post.

107
00:10:08,200 --> 00:10:08,720
Qiu Lin?

108
00:10:09,088 --> 00:10:09,664
Yes.

109
00:10:10,200 --> 00:10:14,080
We were both active members
of the Boss Complaint Group.

110
00:10:14,559 --> 00:10:17,279
Since he became an assistant,
he rarely speaks.

111
00:10:22,799 --> 00:10:23,399
Then I'll eat?

112
00:10:23,679 --> 00:10:24,256
Go ahead.

113
00:10:25,720 --> 00:10:26,440
Try this.

114
00:10:29,080 --> 00:10:30,840
- It's good.
- It's good.

115
00:10:30,840 --> 00:10:31,519
Good, right?

116
00:10:31,519 --> 00:10:32,320
So good.

117
00:10:33,679 --> 00:10:34,360
So good.

118
00:10:42,480 --> 00:10:45,279
Your cooking is as good as ever.

119
00:10:45,559 --> 00:10:48,080
This is good. So is this.

120
00:10:48,559 --> 00:10:49,840
All you know is eat.

121
00:10:49,840 --> 00:10:50,759
None of your business.

122
00:10:51,279 --> 00:10:52,840
Why don't you want to learn?

123
00:10:53,639 --> 00:10:54,639
Then why don't you learn?

124
00:10:54,720 --> 00:10:56,120
I-I'm busy.

125
00:10:56,200 --> 00:10:57,120
Busy about what?

126
00:10:57,360 --> 00:10:58,399
My work is so busy.

127
00:10:58,399 --> 00:10:59,240
No time for that.

128
00:10:59,440 --> 00:11:00,360
Don't talk to me.

129
00:11:00,480 --> 00:11:01,279
Don't bother me.

130
00:11:01,600 --> 00:11:02,519
You too.

131
00:11:14,320 --> 00:11:15,039
I'm full.

132
00:11:16,720 --> 00:11:17,840
Since we're full, then go.

133
00:11:19,200 --> 00:11:19,759
Alright.

134
00:11:21,159 --> 00:11:22,120
Be careful.

135
00:11:23,679 --> 00:11:25,536
Don't worry, Wu Shu is here.

136
00:11:25,536 --> 00:11:27,509
Even if something happens,
she'll handle it.

137
00:11:27,509 --> 00:11:28,720
We won't be the victims.

138
00:11:29,639 --> 00:11:31,440
You are really annoying.

139
00:11:32,120 --> 00:11:33,360
You take a taxi back yourself?

140
00:11:33,720 --> 00:11:34,720
I won't take you back.

141
00:11:34,960 --> 00:11:35,879
How dare you!

142
00:11:37,919 --> 00:11:39,879
Xuan, we're leaving now.

143
00:11:40,080 --> 00:11:42,919
If your mom needs any help,
give me a call.

144
00:11:43,679 --> 00:11:45,080
- Don't worry. Bye.
- Bye.

145
00:11:45,080 --> 00:11:46,639
And me. Just call me.

146
00:11:46,919 --> 00:11:49,840
Even though I'm just an actor,
I guarantee the after-sales service.

147
00:11:59,879 --> 00:12:00,559
Why kick me?

148
00:12:00,559 --> 00:12:01,059
Get going.

149
00:12:01,059 --> 00:12:01,879
Get in the trunk.

150
00:12:02,000 --> 00:12:02,600
What?

151
00:12:02,879 --> 00:12:03,639
Want a beating?

152
00:12:26,455 --> 00:12:28,247
♪In the vast sea of stars♪

153
00:12:28,407 --> 00:12:30,287
♪Flickering neon lights♪

154
00:12:30,487 --> 00:12:33,815
♪Longing spreads
throughout the universe♪

155
00:12:34,327 --> 00:12:36,599
♪Every star is♪

156
00:12:36,887 --> 00:12:40,759
♪My heartbeat for you♪

157
00:12:42,071 --> 00:12:43,895
♪Want to ride the evening breeze♪

158
00:12:44,055 --> 00:12:45,607
♪And land in your arms♪

159
00:12:46,007 --> 00:12:49,463
♪The starry sky is like your eyes♪

160
00:12:49,719 --> 00:12:52,279
♪In the blue sky♪

161
00:12:52,343 --> 00:12:56,471
♪Your smile still lingers♪

162
00:12:57,399 --> 00:13:01,047
♪You are the brightest light
in my regrets♪

163
00:13:01,303 --> 00:13:04,967
♪You are the painful greeting
in my despair♪

164
00:13:05,175 --> 00:13:08,087
♪Can't find a cure♪

165
00:13:08,087 --> 00:13:12,599
♪To love you after we've parted♪

166
00:13:12,791 --> 00:13:16,823
♪You are the time I most want to keep♪

167
00:13:16,823 --> 00:13:20,687
♪The future I strive toward
in the darkness♪

168
00:13:20,687 --> 00:13:22,487
♪Slowly getting closer to you♪

169
00:13:22,583 --> 00:13:27,735
♪How I wish
I could give you my sunshine♪

170
00:13:28,375 --> 00:13:32,087
♪You are the brightest light
in my regrets♪

171
00:13:32,279 --> 00:13:35,031
♪Can't find a cure♪

172
00:13:35,159 --> 00:13:39,799
♪To love you after we've parted♪

173
00:13:39,967 --> 00:13:43,735
♪You are the time I most want to keep♪

174
00:13:43,959 --> 00:13:47,543
♪The future I strive toward
in the darkness♪

175
00:13:47,767 --> 00:13:49,807
♪Slowly getting closer to you♪

176
00:13:49,807 --> 00:13:54,807
♪How I wish
I could give you my sunshine♪
